(1, 21, 'Bristol', 'Bristol Airport Parking', NULL, 'Elite Meet and Greet', NULL, '020 4641 5437  / 07737200551', 'bookings@bristoleliteparking.co.uk', 0.00, '00:00:00', '23:45:00', 0, 12, 24, 'No', 0.00, '', 'Refundable', 'Meet & Greet', NULL, '<p>🚗 Bristol Elite Parking – Meet &amp; Greet Instructions</p><p>📍 Location</p><p>Bristol Airport</p><p>Postcode: BS48 3DY</p><p>Enter via the A38 and follow signs for the Drop &amp; Go Car Park.</p><p>🛫 On Arrival (Drop-Off)</p><p>Call 02046415437</p><p>→ Do this 30 minutes before arriving at the airport.</p><p>Drive to the Drop &amp; Go Car Park</p><p>→ Located next to Departures and clearly signposted.</p><p>A Bristol Elite Parking driver will meet you there.</p><p>Leave £8.50 cash in your car</p><p>→ This covers the airport exit fee (not included in your booking).</p><p>🛬 On Return (Pick-Up)</p><p>Once you have:</p><p>Collected your luggage</p><p>Cleared customs/security</p><p>👉 Call 02046415437</p><p>Go to the Drop &amp; Go Car Park (same place you dropped off your car).</p><p>Your vehicle will be returned to you by a driver.</p><p>You will need £8.50 to exit the car park</p><p>→ Debit cards are also accepted.</p><p>⚠️ Important Information</p><p>🚫 No vans or commercial vehicles accepted</p><p>✈️ Flights are not monitored — Please call when you land</p><p>📞 If your booking time or date changes last minute,</p><p>→ Call 02046415437 to inform the team</p><p>💳 Entry and exit fees for the car park are not included and must be paid by you</p><p>👍 Quick Summary</p><p>Call 30 minutes before arrival</p><p>Meet at Drop &amp; Go Car Park</p><p>Call again after collecting luggage</p><p>Car returned at the same location</p>', NULL, '<p>💳 Entry and exit fees for the car park are not included and must be paid by you</p><p>👍 Quick Summary</p><p>Call 30 minutes before arrival</p><p>Meet at Drop &amp; Go Car Park</p><p>Call again after collecting luggage</p><p>Car returned at the same location</p>', '<p>🚗 Bristol Elite Parking – Meet &a